text: cng klaw theid (muhammad) wa xo brrda phu di rab khamphir ! Cng mayang thxykha hnung sung theatheiym kan rahwang rea læa phwk than khux wa rea ca mi khea ra sakkara nxkcak phraxngkh theanan læa rea ca mi hı sing hnung sing dı pen phakhi kab phraxngkh læa phwk rea bang khn k ca mi yudthux xik bang khn pen phracea xun ca kxallxh læw hak phwk khea phinhlanghı k cng klaw theid wa phwk than cng pen phyan dwywa thæcring phwk rea pen phu nxm tam
